        "markdown_formatted": "## Meeting Purpose\n\n[Tech check and platform walkthrough for Marcel Santilli's upcoming workshop at DEMAND event.](https://fathom.video/share/3kPEHbHF-JnN47XBzyWoEK-q3VsxzP9n?tab=summary&timestamp=0.0)\n\n## Key Takeaways\n\n  - [Marcel is experienced with virtual events (hosted 3 conferences, including one with 30k attendees)](https://fathom.video/share/3kPEHbHF-JnN47XBzyWoEK-q3VsxzP9n?tab=summary&timestamp=52.0)\n  - [Goldcast platform will be used; Marcel to familiarize with login, navigation, and backstage access](https://fathom.video/share/3kPEHbHF-JnN47XBzyWoEK-q3VsxzP9n?tab=summary&timestamp=30.0)\n  - [Speaker link provided; tech check and profile setup required before each login](https://fathom.video/share/3kPEHbHF-JnN47XBzyWoEK-q3VsxzP9n?tab=summary&timestamp=186.0)\n\n## Topics\n\n### Platform Access and Navigation\n\n  - [Speakers use a unique link to access the Goldcast platform](https://fathom.video/share/3kPEHbHF-JnN47XBzyWoEK-q3VsxzP9n?tab=summary&timestamp=95.0)\n  - [Landing page: Click \"Enter Event\" in bottom right corner](https://fathom.video/share/3kPEHbHF-JnN47XBzyWoEK-q3VsxzP9n?tab=summary&timestamp=99.0)\n  - [Mandatory tech check: camera, microphone, audio, virtual background options](https://fathom.video/share/3kPEHbHF-JnN47XBzyWoEK-q3VsxzP9n?tab=summary&timestamp=108.0)\n  - [Profile setup/verification required at each login](https://fathom.video/share/3kPEHbHF-JnN47XBzyWoEK-q3VsxzP9n?tab=summary&timestamp=138.0)\n  - [Navigate to Agenda, scroll to session, click \"Enter Backstage\"](https://fathom.video/share/3kPEHbHF-JnN47XBzyWoEK-q3VsxzP9n?tab=summary&timestamp=163.0)\n\n### Speaker Experience\n\n  - [Marcel has extensive virtual event experience (3 conferences hosted)](https://fathom.video/share/3kPEHbHF-JnN47XBzyWoEK-q3VsxzP9n?tab=summary&timestamp=40.0)\n  - [Familiar with general process, new to Goldcast specifically](https://fathom.video/share/3kPEHbHF-JnN47XBzyWoEK-q3VsxzP9n?tab=summary&timestamp=46.0)\n  - [Previous event managed 30,000 attendees](https://fathom.video/share/3kPEHbHF-JnN47XBzyWoEK-q3VsxzP9n?tab=summary&timestamp=52.0)\n\n### Technical Considerations\n\n  - [No virtual background preferred for natural look](https://fathom.video/share/3kPEHbHF-JnN47XBzyWoEK-q3VsxzP9n?tab=summary&timestamp=115.0)\n  - [Screen sharing will be available and tested during tech check](https://fathom.video/share/3kPEHbHF-JnN47XBzyWoEK-q3VsxzP9n?tab=summary&timestamp=130.0)\n  - [Potential conflicts between Zoom and Goldcast camera usage noted](https://fathom.video/share/3kPEHbHF-JnN47XBzyWoEK-q3VsxzP9n?tab=summary&timestamp=71.0)\n\n### Event Preparation\n\n  - [Speaker link shared via chat and calendar invite for easy access](https://fathom.video/share/3kPEHbHF-JnN47XBzyWoEK-q3VsxzP9n?tab=summary&timestamp=188.0)\n  - [Mia will meet Marcel in the backstage area on event day](https://fathom.video/share/3kPEHbHF-JnN47XBzyWoEK-q3VsxzP9n?tab=summary&timestamp=178.0)\n\n## Next Steps\n\n  - Marcel to use provided link to access Goldcast platform\n  - Complete tech check and profile setup\n  - Familiarize with navigation to workshop session and backstage area\n  - Prepare for workshop delivery on DEMAND event day\n"
